<text id="02-output-contract" title="Verbatim → Backlog — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="700" depth="essential">
  <summary>Pins the shape of `BacklogCard` and the cluster intermediate.</summary>

  <section title="BacklogCard required fields">
    <list>
      <item>`card_id` — string</item>
      <item>`title_job_story` — string in "When ..., I want ..., so I can ..." format</item>
      <item>`cluster_id` — string</item>
      <item>`quotes_attached` — array (≥ 2) of `{source_id, source_type, source_url, timestamp, body_verbatim}`</item>
      <item>`rice` — object `{reach_pct, impact_1_to_3, confidence_pct, effort_tshirt, score}`</item>
      <item>`evidence_status` — enum {sufficient, insufficient, single-source-risk}</item>
      <item>`opportunity_solution_tree_node` — string (parent opportunity if structured)</item>
      <item>`added_at` — ISO-8601</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Cluster required fields">
    <list>
      <item>`cluster_id` — string</item>
      <item>`statement_count` — integer</item>
      <item>`cosine_similarity_mean` — number 0-1</item>
      <item>`status` — enum {watchlist, ready, split-needed}</item>
      <item>`representative_statement` — verbatim text closest to centroid</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <antipattern>
      <description>BacklogCard with `quotes_attached.length &lt; 2`.</description>
      <reason>Violates r2.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>`title_job_story` lacking one of: "When", "I want", "so I can".</description>
      <reason>Violates r4 framing.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>`title_job_story` references a persona ("As a user / manager / founder...").</description>
      <reason>Violates r4 anti-persona rule.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>`rice.confidence_pct &gt; 80` AND `quotes_attached.length &lt; 3`.</description>
      <reason>Inflated confidence; the rule requires both quote count + recency to drive confidence.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>Quotes paraphrased or summarised in `body_verbatim`.</description>
      <reason>Violates r2 verbatim attachment.</reason>
    </antipattern>
  </section>

  <section title="Allowed transformations">
    <list>
      <item>Trim quotes &gt; 500 chars to first 200 + "[...]" + last 50, preserving specifics.</item>
      <item>Anonymise source_user names while keeping source_id.</item>
      <item>Aggregate multiple Discord messages from same user into one source entry with thread_url.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="templates/backlog-card.json">BacklogCard JSON Schema.</reference>
  <reference path="templates/job-story.md">Job-Story template.</reference>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Card title in Job-Story format.</item>
      <item>≥ 2 verbatim quotes with source URLs.</item>
      <item>RICE fields all sourced.</item>
      <item>Cluster status drives card creation (watchlist clusters do NOT generate cards).</item>
      <item>Cards link back to their cluster.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
